<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>cold for someone • cold to someone</xh5><p> <i>cold for someone—</i>is used of smth. not warm enough for a person: The water was too <u>cold for</u> me, and I decided not to bathe that day.</p><p> <i>cold to someone</i>—(also: cold with someone) said of smb. who is not kind or friendly to a person: He was <u>cold to</u> his son that morning.</p> </entry>
